<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03E687FCFFA9FF8949ABFB53FB99FF78:8E906031FFAAFF894B65FF6DFB84FF17" box="[865,1082,142,166]" country="Tanzania" name="Afrotropical region" pageId="10" pageNumber="875" stateProvince="Kilimanjaro">Afrotropical region</location>
